        <p>Thank you for installing Phonedeck.</p>
        <p>Please follow a few final steps to grant all the permissions your users need. Alternatively you can <a href="https://phonedeck.com/documentation/" target="_blank">read Phonedeck's user's and administrator's guide.</a></p>
