                    Use Phonedeck to speed up your everyday workflow. It saves you time and boosts your productivity. Find all important features in one view: MyPhone, Task list, History, Calendar, Contact search and Scratchpad.
                </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>check your today tasks by choosing the right date in the calendar</li>
