                    <p>
                        You are now able to control your iPhone remotely from the Windows browser. Install the Phonedeck Bluetooth application on your computer and just pair the devices. You are ready to make, take and log the calls directly from the Windows browser or take Salesforce on the road using your iPhone. Have your call workflow at hand wherever you are.
